spec.jcraft.anubis.info.details:
PASSIVE: Bloodlust
Landing blows on opponents speeds up Anubis' attacks up to 2x, with +0.2x per hit.
Not hitting opponents reduces Bloodlust by one stack every 4 seconds.

PASSIVES: Hamon breath
Tap Barrage to toggle whether the next move uses Hamon or not.
Hold Ultimate to charge Hamon. Executing a move during breath also activates the Hamon variant.
